beer.beer_description:
Another neighbourhood collaboration, this time with our friends at Kerbside Brewing.

A new take on an old school West Coast IPA, building on the malt base of Kerbside's Too Juicy Pale we layered in Centennial, Simcoe, Amarillo and Azacca hops to create what we think is a nice little homage to the beers that got most of us into this business.
